{"tid":531162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個令自己睇開d既諗法","createTime":"2018-01-16T13:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T13:41:21.000Z","uid":58333,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e47cdfe8428a294ff6ffc9688b4846337295f4","tid":531162,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"見好多人都好執著 搞到人生好唔開心<br />\n不如大家分享下點令自己睇得開d呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令自己過得開心d<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n-如果分左手 就同自己講<br />\n 唔係你既就唔係你 下個會更好<br />\n-做錯事 俾人鬧 唔好諗自己有幾慘 <br />\n而要試下諗自己從中可以點再改善 做得更好<br />\n-俾同事中傷 就繼續做好自己本份 等睇佢仆街俾人搞返轉頭既一日<br />\n-發現自己唔夠人叻 就諗做人唔好太貪心 <br />\n有今時今日成就 個天已經係比多左自己 <br />\n無謂再向上比 人比人 比死人"},{"pid":"f66ff3da421a0749aee43793604d94d113a95dc6","tid":531162,"uid":86037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e47cdfe8428a294ff6ffc9688b4846337295f4","tid":531162,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"見好多人都好執著 搞到人生好唔開心<br />\n不如大家分享下點令自己睇得開d呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令自己過得開心d<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n-如果分左手 就同自己講<br />\n 唔係你既就唔係你 下個會更好<br />\n-做錯事 俾人鬧 唔好諗自己有幾慘 <br />\n而要試下諗自己從中可以點再改善 做得更好<br />\n-俾同事中傷 就繼續做好自己本份 等睇佢仆街俾人搞返轉頭既一日<br />\n-發現自己唔夠人叻 就諗做人唔好太貪心 <br />\n有今時今日成就 個天已經係比多左自己 <br />\n無謂再向上比 人比人 比死人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:42:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"25c7cc5453da0d2add14e791f6b3c636aba07dff","tid":531162,"uid":86037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"my : 無慾則剛"},{"pid":"1f9e3f8fde95cd813458172b6e4e7427db5a15b1","tid":531162,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"你睇我好 我睇你好"},{"pid":"2d0910c911c1ad1395a6fde8afc53219f5635656","tid":531162,"uid":58333,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f9e3f8fde95cd813458172b6e4e7427db5a15b1","tid":531162,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"你睇我好 我睇你好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"岩! <br />\n唔好只係睇人地風光果面 要睇埋人地背後既苦/辛酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c91536f2a15d18a2d0e109659cf031abb83954","tid":531162,"uid":7954,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18525f370eaab518ee0a2d9d077c74e4eeb3fd29","tid":531162,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"得之我幸 不得我命"},{"pid":"3218952835f6abc7d7721fc1bc25a5baad8be41d","tid":531162,"uid":166996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"樓主 支持你開呢類型po 散發正能量👍"},{"pid":"d77fb295d10556c7ba0805e83bec58d97b1e55b6","tid":531162,"uid":167190,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T22:43:50.000Z","msg":"明明你好想要一樣嘢，但現在嘅你得唔到，你就不斷同自己講：「我唔需要、我唔需要、我唔需要⋯⋯」你講得越多，你就更加得唔到呢樣嘢。你以為可以呃到自己，你以為咁樣就叫做「成熟」「識諗」。<br />\n<br />\n但正因為你逃避自己嘅慾望，你跌入咗下沉嘅漩渦，無法翻身。你內心好渴求得到，但你嘅言行都推開緊得到佢嘅機會，於是你活得越來越痛苦。然後，你期望講更多次「我唔需要」就可以填補內心的空虛，結果係令內心越來越痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n不敢正視內心，過住表裡不一的生活，明明好想要一樣嘢，但就自己親手推開晒可以得到嘅機會。呢種「成熟」同「識諗」，表面上好似幫緊你去「睇開啲」，實際上不知害咗幾多人，每日要過住逃避內心的痛苦生活。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/theKingCliffy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2FtheKingCliffy%2F&d=Pm9R%2F%2BcaKo8sz3dYKC1zZDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1da96499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/theKingCliffy/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都忍左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f728e5325f540f81787060979d1d5eb629f7871a","tid":531162,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3218952835f6abc7d7721fc1bc25a5baad8be41d","tid":531162,"uid":166996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"樓主 支持你開呢類型po 散發正能量👍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b019fdc078841f3b9ba93ac37c32f8abca38bc","tid":531162,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:34:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fb00def33d1c429f137e7d41078b6f83f65516f","tid":531162,"uid":115644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"命裏有時終須有 命裏無時莫強求 <br />\n<br />\n好多野整定的<br />\n<br />\n到既時候你想唔要都唔得 唔係你就點都唔係你"},{"pid":"f70739e3d44c9dc3a4a7a72f49d85889dee5884c","tid":531162,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1c91536f2a15d18a2d0e109659cf031abb83954","tid":531162,"uid":7954,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估我想架咩"},{"pid":"21a20e72a01990c08599947673f548b9a99cddf8","tid":531162,"uid":2736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e9ddb7f5c4e50ae67c3f75d7309435ed674359","tid":531162,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"只要是石頭,去到哪裡也不會發光"},{"pid":"afa513ddb860af9314bf4df8f8f9617a696c02ad","tid":531162,"uid":111811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"係你就係你 唔係你就唔係你<br />\n盡左力 其餘交由上天決定"},{"pid":"2c8ded3d6b333439977a9a8da77893ee1f4fb73b","tid":531162,"uid":165450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"我會諗, 可能下一秒行出街都俾車撞死, 而家梗係開開心心咁過左佢就算"},{"pid":"722f22632ee52246eb1b141ad2239be4b55c5d39","tid":531162,"uid":61050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔撚好同人比 只要自己係進步緊嘅就夠啦<img sr